From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Richard M <richard@rmoser.ca>
Date: Mon, 17 Feb 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] aaw2b: extract device tree into dtsi for reuse

Extract aaw2b.dts content into aaw2b.dtsi so the hardware description
can be reused or extended without duplicating the full board definition.
The aaw2b.dts becomes a minimal stub that includes the new dtsi.

--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/aaw2b.dts	2026-04-16 18:53:10.238690064 +0000
